---
title: Mexican Pork Tacos with Corn, Pineapple Slaw and Creamy Baja Sauce
description: These bright and colourful Mexican pork tacos tick every box, with a warming spice blend for the meat, a sweet and zesty pineapple slaw, all topped with creamy Baja sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tacos-au-porc-a-la-mexicaine-9ffb8735.jpg
